canonical:
  title: 寄正叔
  author: 禔
  language: lzh
  text: 讀書三月不窺園未覺園林綠已繁梅子欲成春自去謾將幽思立黃昏
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 寄正叔
  author: 禔
  language: lzh
  text: 讀書三月不窺園。未覺園林綠已繁。梅子欲成春自去。謾將幽思立黃昏。
korean:
  title: 기 정숙
  author: 제
  language: kor
  text: |-
    글 읽어 석달 동안 동산을 엿보잖아
    온 숲에 푸른 빛이 성한 줄을 몰랐노라
    매실은 맺고 봄은 절로 가려는데
    깊은 생각 부질없이 황혼에 서 있노라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1460_010_0180&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 제(禔) : '
    value: 양녕대군. 왕족은 성을 안 썼다.
  - key: '[주-D001] 富林君 : '
    value: 저본에는 없다. 저본의 원목차에 근거하여 보충하였다.
english:
  title: To Jeong-suk
  author: Je
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Three months immersed in reading,
    I have not glimpsed the garden.
    Yet the grove grows verdant without my knowing—
    the green abundance has already flourished.

    The plum fruits ripen and spring departs on its own.
    In vain I stand at dusk
    with my profound thoughts.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: The speaker's deep concentration on study has made him oblivious to the passage of seasons and the blooming of nature around him.
  - key: ''
    value: The ripening plum and departing spring suggest the transience of time and opportunity—a meditation on what is lost through singular focus.
